Common applications and/or configuration files:

1. daemon - scripts and configuration files of the archive daemon,
            see Manual, ch 6.2.3

2. engine - configuration file of the archive engine, 
            see Manual, ch. 3
            
3. indextool - command-line tool for combining multiple indices 
               into a Master file, see Manual, ch. 5.1

4. pva - configuration file of the RPC-based data retrieval service, 
         see Manual, ch 4.3.3

